    "description": "<br>您可以在 <strong>'Bazaar Simulator'</strong> 的序章版本中开始管理您的市场，并享受有限的体验。别忘了将游戏的完整版本添加到您的愿望单并关注。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >传统秤系统</h2>使用市场上使用的传统秤准确称量您的水果和蔬菜。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/c39cb8e77194d5dfb9a7d152c5ef8b09.poster.avif?t=1753376621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/c39cb8e77194d5dfb9a7d152c5ef8b09.webm?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/c39cb8e77194d5dfb9a7d152c5ef8b09.mp4?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >库存订购和管理</h2>购买您的库存，组织它们的位置，并将它们从箱子转移到摊位。请记住，水果和蔬菜会随着时间的推移开始腐烂。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/dfd7cdcde7124e88c9707b79a66a68d5.poster.avif?t=1753376621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/dfd7cdcde7124e88c9707b79a66a68d5.webm?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/dfd7cdcde7124e88c9707b79a66a68d5.mp4?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >互动销售体验</h2>帮助客户选择并管理现金及通过二维码或IBAN支付。确保每个客户都满意离开，创造回头客和活跃的市场氛围。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/eb3ffe9decea696c5c273d522188d5c5.poster.avif?t=1753376621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/eb3ffe9decea696c5c273d522188d5c5.webm?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/eb3ffe9decea696c5c273d522188d5c5.mp4?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >适应市场波动</h2>在价格低廉时购买产品，并在动态市场环境中设定有竞争力的销售价格。通过平衡利润率和客户满意度来发展您的业务。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >投资与扩展</h2>随着利润的增加，投资于您的市场。扩展您的市场，升级您的摊位，并改善购物环境。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/361622518cfc3c0f8fa69fd9473c0ef1.poster.avif?t=1753376621\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/361622518cfc3c0f8fa69fd9473c0ef1.webm?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3033810/extras/361622518cfc3c0f8fa69fd9473c0ef1.mp4?t=1753376621\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从柠檬摊到市场帝国</h2>在 <strong>&quot;Bazaar Simulator&quot;</strong> 中，每一个选择都会影响您的成功。您会从柠檬摊开始建立自己的市场帝国，还是会继续做一个柠檬商？",
